snippet.title: ItsNat, Natural AJAX Java Web Framework
snippet.description: ItsNat is a Component based AJAX Java Web Application Framework.No XML programming,no mixed view/code,no custom JavaScript.Only pure HTML,pure Java and server centric Swing-like programming with W3C standards where "The Browser is The Server"
